Wireframes = BLUEPRINTS for UI (structure only, NO colors/fonts/images) and save 100s dev hours by catching issues pre-code
1. HIERARCHY: Biggest = Most Important
   - Overall goal → 48pt
   - Secondary → 24pt  
   - Details → 14pt
   - Use SIZE + POSITION (not color)

2. CLARITY: Can stranger understand in 5 sec?
   - Label EVERYTHING ("Button", "Search", "Error State")
   - No ambiguity → "Click → Shows results"

3. CONSISTENCY: Same patterns everywhere
   - All buttons same shape/location
   - Same nav across screens
   - Reuse components (header, footer)

4. MOBILE FIRST: Design phone → scale up
